<div id="content">
  <h1>Mission Statement </h1>
  <p> The center members conduct research in theory and algorithms for optimization, develop models for novel
    application areas, and create optimization software and modeling tools. Current application areas include: Energy systems, machine learning, optimal design, healthcare, transportation and communication networks, and computational finance.</p>
